# Thyroid Disease Prediction Using Machine Learning
## Om Yadav
### Domain: Healthcare
### Tech Stack: Python, Machine Learning

## Objective
To predict thyroid disease using machine learning techniques.

## Dataset
Contains 3772 entries with 30 features related to thyroid conditions.

## Data Preprocessing
- Handled missing values and categorical data
- Techniques used:
  - KNN Imputer
  - One-hot encoding
- Balanced the dataset using:
  - SMOTENC
  - RandomOverSampler

## Models Used
- Logistic Regression
- Support Vector Machine (SVM)
- K-Nearest Neighbors (KNN)
- Decision Tree
- Random Forest

## Results
**Best Model:** Random Forest with an accuracy of 99.25%  
**Evaluation Metrics:** Accuracy, Precision, Recall, F1 Score

## Conclusion
The Random Forest model performed the best, making it suitable for predicting thyroid disease.